{"pageProps":{"entry":{"id":"local-the-softness-of-silicon-valley","title":"The Softness of Silicon Valley","date":"2023-02-10","slug":"the-softness-of-silicon-valley","categories":["Life","Work","Identity"],"mood":"Introspective","summary":"I thought getting in was the hard part. It wasn't. The hard part was learning how to exist in a world where no one tells you if you're enough.","wordCount":639,"location":"Silicon Valley","source":"local","mdxSources":{"en":{"compiledSource":"var u=Object.defineProperty,d=Object.defineProperties;var w=Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors;var n=Object.getOwnPropertySymbols;var r=Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty,p=Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable;var s=(e,t,a)=>t in e?u(e,t,{enumerable:!0,configurable:!0,writable:!0,value:a}):e[t]=a,i=(e,t)=>{for(var a in t||(t={}))r.call(t,a)&&s(e,a,t[a]);if(n)for(var a of n(t))p.call(t,a)&&s(e,a,t[a]);return e},h=(e,t)=>d(e,w(t));var l=(e,t)=>{var a={};for(var o in e)r.call(e,o)&&t.indexOf(o)<0&&(a[o]=e[o]);if(e!=null&&n)for(var o of n(e))t.indexOf(o)<0&&p.call(e,o)&&(a[o]=e[o]);return a};const layoutProps={},MDXLayout=\"wrapper\";function MDXContent(a){var o=a,{components:e}=o,t=l(o,[\"components\"]);return mdx(MDXLayout,h(i(i({},layoutProps),t),{components:e,mdxType:\"MDXLayout\"}),mdx(\"h1\",null,\"The Softness of Silicon Valley\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I thought Silicon Valley would be hard.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Sharp people. High standards. Constant pressure.\nA place where you either perform or you\\u2019re out.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I was ready for that version of the world.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`What I wasn\\u2019t ready for\\u2026\nwas how soft it felt.`),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"Politeness as a System\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"No one tells you you\\u2019re wrong here.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"They say things like:\"),mdx(\"ul\",null,mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"\\u201CThat\\u2019s an interesting approach.\\u201D\"),mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"\\u201CLet\\u2019s explore that a bit more.\\u201D\"),mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"\\u201CI wonder if there\\u2019s another angle.\\u201D\")),mdx(\"p\",null,`In Taiwan, feedback had edges.\nYou knew when you did poorly.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Here, everything was rounded.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`At first, it felt kind. Then it became confusing.\nThen, slowly, it became exhausting.`),mdx(\"p\",null,`Because if no one tells you you're wrong\\u2014\nno one tells you you're right either.`),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"The Missing Signal\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I didn\\u2019t realize how much I depended on clear signals.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Grades. Rankings. Results.\nEven failure had structure.`),mdx(\"p\",null,`But here, feedback was abstract. Performance was implied.\nYou were expected to `,mdx(\"em\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"just know\"),\".\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"And I didn\\u2019t.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"So I started filling in the gaps myself.\"),mdx(\"ul\",null,mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"If no one praised it, maybe it wasn\\u2019t good\"),mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"If feedback was vague, maybe I missed something\"),mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"If I wasn\\u2019t sure, I assumed the worst\")),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It wasn\\u2019t rational.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"But it was familiar.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"A Different Kind of Hunger\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Looking back, I wasn\\u2019t just trying to do good work.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I was trying to feel \",mdx(\"em\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"recognized\"),\".\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Not in a loud, obvious way\\u2014\nbut in the quiet, human way:`),mdx(\"p\",null,`Someone noticing.\nSomeone saying, \\u201Cthis is good.\\u201D\nSomeone making it clear that I belonged.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I didn\\u2019t have the language for it at the time.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"So I translated it into effort.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Work harder. Stay later. Fix more things.\nBe useful enough that no one questions you.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It worked\\u2014on the surface.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"But underneath, nothing was being resolved.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"Luck, Misunderstood\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"If you looked at my life from the outside, it was simple:\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"A kid from Taiwan makes it to Silicon Valley.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Lucky.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"That word came up a lot.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"And I didn\\u2019t disagree.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"But luck hides the more uncomfortable truth:\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Getting in doesn\\u2019t mean you\\u2019re ready.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It just means you\\u2019re allowed in the room.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`What you bring with you\\u2014your habits, your fears, your ways of making sense of the world\\u2014\nthose don\\u2019t upgrade automatically.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"They just get\\u2026 exposed.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"Learning What Was Never Taught\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The hardest part wasn\\u2019t the work.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It was learning things that weren\\u2019t written anywhere:\"),mdx(\"ul\",null,mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"How to read between the lines\"),mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"How to ask for feedback without feeling like you're failing\"),mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"How to separate your work from your worth\"),mdx(\"li\",{parentName:\"ul\"},\"How to accept that \\u201Cno negative feedback\\u201D might actually mean \\u201Cyou\\u2019re doing fine\\u201D\")),mdx(\"p\",null,\"These weren\\u2019t technical problems.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"They were human ones.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"And I was underprepared.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"The Quiet Realization\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"At some point, I started noticing a pattern.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The people who did well weren\\u2019t always the smartest.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"They were the ones who seemed\\u2026 at ease.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`They could take feedback without shrinking.\nThey could speak without over-calculating.\nThey didn\\u2019t need constant confirmation to keep going.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It wasn\\u2019t confidence in the loud sense.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It was something steadier.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Something internal.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"What This Chapter Really Was\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I thought I came here to become a better engineer.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"And I did.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"But that wasn\\u2019t the real work.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The real work was more uncomfortable than that:\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Learning that competence doesn\\u2019t automatically create security.\nLearning that achievement doesn\\u2019t automatically create belonging.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"And slowly, painfully\\u2014\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Learning that the thing I was chasing in work\nwas never just about work.`),mdx(\"hr\",null),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I was more fortunate than I understood.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Not just because I made it here\\u2014\nbut because this place revealed something I had been able to avoid seeing for a long time.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"A need I didn\\u2019t know how to name.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`A version of myself\nthat needed more than success to feel whole.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The next chapter is where that realization starts to change how I live.\"))}MDXContent.isMDXComponent=!0;\n","scope":{}},"zh":{"compiledSource":"var o=Object.defineProperty,N=Object.defineProperties;var s=Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors;var t=Object.getOwnPropertySymbols;var u=Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty,i=Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable;var r=(p,l,e)=>l in p?o(p,l,{enumerable:!0,configurable:!0,writable:!0,value:e}):p[l]=e,n=(p,l)=>{for(var e in l||(l={}))u.call(l,e)&&r(p,e,l[e]);if(t)for(var e of t(l))i.call(l,e)&&r(p,e,l[e]);return p},m=(p,l)=>N(p,s(l));var h=(p,l)=>{var e={};for(var a in p)u.call(p,a)&&l.indexOf(a)<0&&(e[a]=p[a]);if(p!=null&&t)for(var a of t(p))l.indexOf(a)<0&&i.call(p,a)&&(e[a]=p[a]);return e};const layoutProps={},MDXLayout=\"wrapper\";function MDXContent(e){var a=e,{components:p}=a,l=h(a,[\"components\"]);return mdx(MDXLayout,m(n(n({},layoutProps),l),{components:p,mdxType:\"MDXLayout\"}),mdx(\"h1\",null,\"\\u77FD\\u8C37\\u7684\\u67D4\\u8EDF\"),mdx(\"p\",null